  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;line-height:1.75;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 2 []\">\n    <div style=\"border-top:none;padding:10px;border-right:none;margin:20px 0;display:block;line-height:26px;border-bottom:none;word-spacing:normal;outline:0;overflow:auto;max-width:100%;border-left:8px solid #222222;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;hyphens:auto;text-align:left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">当Agent进入真实工作流</span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622982\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=575a01a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkRJbqEhlcwPf8mKib5yHHT9OTlxaIbDcWDbZ7puxFFlhWle0NRicWVpPcq78Ob6FnetDtMwSSMnSTic8BeNKfuyWxjJ5lGsbnaibs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">👦🏻 作者: Jack</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">🥷 编辑: Koji</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">🧑‍🎨 排版: NCon</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501618718\" data-ratio=\"0.12129629629629629\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=09352c14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FFFcNSoQ3KicuV7H25k8TfssXv4QnhFalhKhckCt5TgQMvm1yicxz4CI1fLagAOt6l6ozg3reVAywAkLMgBWfGXbQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">3月7日，OpenClaw 创始人 Peter Steinberger 在 X 上转发了一份 PinchBench 榜单：专门测「哪个模型跑 OpenClaw 最强」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这条推文获得了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;42 万次</span>浏览。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">32 个模型参与评测，MiniMax M2.1 以 95.4% 的成功率排名第二，仅次于 Google Gemini 3 Flash。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622963\" data-ratio=\"0.925\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c45a5a45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPql9YzbsB6TaSdHscnPiblCHNciao5eB86yIJBmZAgticUU44osIkibWatKGkAtkWicIumicqNdJrMmep4cN1JVNO2Pq2gLcUgrnXzJuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们之前也测试过MiniMax M2.5 这个模型：《春节，MiniMax的王炸牌来了》，从 OpenClaw 私人助理到前端网页到 iOS App 原型，表现很稳。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在 M2.7 来了。但这次的升级，和之前「模型变强了」的故事不太一样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次，我们没有去跑通用 benchmark，而是直接把 M2.7 接进了「十字路口」自己的工作流里，让它在我们真实的工作中干活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:40px 0;font-weight:bold;display:block;width:fit-content;font-size:17px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥</span></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">公众号一键自动排版</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">十字路口内容团队平时用 Notion 来协作创作内容，但每次发公众号都要手动搬运和重新排版，一直是个体力活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次我们直接让 M2.7 从零开始，帮我们开发一个 Chrome 扩展：</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">一键把 Notion 文档转换成微信公众号格式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"border:1px solid #f0f0f0;padding:10px;margin:20px 10px;color:#333;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:5px;box-shadow:rgba(0,0,0,.3) 0px 2px 10px;overflow-x:auto;font-family:Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;text-align:left;\"></p>\n   <pre style=\"padding:0;margin:0;overflow-x:auto;\"><code style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:normal;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.65;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发一个chrome的插件，在飞书或者notion的文章页面打开时</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">转换成公众号的排版格式，可以一键粘贴，图片使用</span><span><span leaf=\"\">base64</span></span><span leaf=\"\">；</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">我会提供给你目前排版的json格式给你</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚开始，M2.7 清晰的识别了这个项目的难度，自动启动了Plan Mode，把任务拆成了几个阶段。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622972\" data-ratio=\"0.7425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a5b414f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnouM1oXUUcibl1da17Ou1C2FmCeYF1nu9Hdib4xj0F4BqKbXV69vebK57m8BSted5tYJsrfLhINibzwxVPEL3BOA2WiabUq6mSiaibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里有一个细节值得单独说。开发 Chrome 扩展的过程中，需要和浏览器做联调，传统流程里，开发者得手动打开 DevTools、一层层翻 DOM 结构，费时费力</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622969\" data-ratio=\"0.5388888888888889\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1299a249&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkrbTXZp3e1Rjf6AuvjOKLHNlbGwickQESPA063nrc9HRB4adSz9uuF5WAJjdt9GicEY8gCicibUesHJibYMTnBqu0NavOHgAwjeSj0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">M2.7 的做法不一样：它自己通过命令行启动了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Chrome 远程调试模式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，用 CDP 协议直接抓取页面的 DOM 结构，在 console 里分析 Notion 的渲染逻辑，然后才动手写代码。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">遇到样式问题，它会自己回到 DevTools 排查，改完继续推进，全程不需要人工介入。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622960\" data-ratio=\"0.17777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa2b6b3e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkuVhoicC4GZcKXStg76e2icAQbcWYiajziaHTHlc9qZEwKI9s34M7zLQQqTYacLt4K3EJeYasNduP60tdiaM6JJtwOkGwBbL7zWKibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从项目搭建到核心功能到调试修复，大概跑了半天，基本是它自己完成的，我们只做了最后的微调。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最终 M2.7 还通过 CLI 工具自动把代码 PR 到了 GitHub 上，全程我们只手动提供了一个 GitHub Token</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622962\" data-ratio=\"0.5222222222222223\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b32b4da&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmUYdHSYcIKiaRib5nmECvrL1zuGEKQJByM0iabpecLCU4y9Lyj7s5OZRDCvvG3TH11jb3ndibXibfxN8QPvdVLIdLWWiaYmVWgPPIz8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">来看最终成品：在文章页面打开插件，点「一键转换」，几秒钟搞定，复制粘贴到公众号后台就行。</span></p>\n   <div data-video-src=\"https://file.notion.so/f/f/b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d/1cf86381-dd3f-40e9-b2d7-70082458dccd/3月18日(3).mov?table=block&amp;id=3278e8f5-8ed1-80ae-a44f-c377e3a34291&amp;spaceId=b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d&amp;expirationTimestamp=1774000800000&amp;signature=vYmy5Q7O-O-NRGmH98WTmzoJiXcL1YkZz_KmRy4Df9s\" data-video-thumb=\"https://file.notion.so/f/f/b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d/8e7e67fb-8419-4744-ad0b-bd49281a22cc/3月18日(3).mov_thumbnail.jpg?table=block&amp;id=3278e8f5-8ed1-80ae-a44f-c377e3a34291&amp;spaceId=b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d&amp;expirationTimestamp=1774000800000&amp;signature=MowWFTkAMm9oeDuM8BSRn1fuQQ79ZPFwvqUY04gT4nI\" style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它甚至还顺手做了两件附加的事：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、把「十字路口」现有的公众号排版规则整理成了一个可视化网页，每种元素的样式对比一目了然</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、做了一个带一键下载功能的安装教程页面，每一步都写得很清楚。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622961\" data-ratio=\"0.49444444444444446\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8afddb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmVCMmCW05c5amibkX5gWibu0ic3a4HSdpiapZLcTiatYU9icQHlCMFOX9icoN7ibibWcKLXjbs1pF79GugcvpdxhcmThqiciaxVxdibJCFyxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49444444444444446\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622959\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b24a65e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqlDYhqy30q62CDqr12J7Qd9eC16ICrIOTLdFRsdicvEeFGsUH4OyvW0Ld0RiaWQ93GvOVkwGwDZfNib8shXiaiblWtvOgux4R7vD1AY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI Podcast 监控/下载工具</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们除了公众号，还有一档播客：「十字路口 Crossing」，我们长期关注 AI 创业者、产品和行业变化，在小宇宙上有近 10 万订阅。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们每天需要保证有大量的信息输入，所以我们需要长期监控 AI 行业的头部播客，作为选题调研和学习资料。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了效率，我们自己写了一个批量下载工具，可以直接从 YouTube 上把播客音视频拉下来归档。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4759259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622964\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e92822a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmlZl8TticHXiaJN2qZ3uScQIicbxSAlSbB0icqFvEEs1zBq0dsOsfdgzibRL5AcOS5za3TL9ATibshal6Xe5kQ2R7yqHxZgWzJjwicjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次我们想做一件事：把这个下载工具接进 OpenClaw，变成一个龙虾可以直接调用的 Skill。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把仓库交给 M2.7 之后，它没有闷头部署，而是先把项目结构、依赖关系和运行方式完整过了一遍。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622965\" data-ratio=\"1.098148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb3eef04&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmwjz7RDmrx17MI0tET2ApmDc1SPibpKR0ibpgempQzH2FSBzia2Y33p4RRImz0nWpW5EcHibTibs1t8NUAoKF8YE9mGnMqA3gR4z1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">过程中它还主动去查了 yt-dlp 近几个版本的 changelog，发现 cookie 处理逻辑已经改了，于是回到代码里把调用方式一起修掉，再把 Docker 里的版本号锁死，顺手把未来可能踩的坑也补上了</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个排查路径很清晰：先读项目结构 → 查上游变更 → 定位本地影响 → 修复 → 防御性加固，确实像一个干过几年的后端工程师的习惯。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在这个工具已经正式跑在我们的 OpenClaw 上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们试一下把一个月前Lex Fridman访谈OpenClaw创始人Peter Steinberger的播客视频下载下来</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">此时只需要跟「十字路口小助手」说：“帮我下载Lex Fridman访谈Peter Steinberger的播客视频”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622967\" data-ratio=\"1.0703703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=435622c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmckAiaBKJL9A6E02m3D8llgwbLwtyYJcVqN3MHYLejic0niamkIPmlfAPC1ffTYbIBEqVWQET5aEmzI8gbfsJehoIloK50KtB2Ds%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">中途可以随时问进度，大概不到 5 分钟，一期 3 小时的对谈视频就下载到文件夹里了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622970\" data-ratio=\"0.4648148148148148\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=04c4f7fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnNCVNpqI8FLCcrJMicat9KtGmDekmsuibqbu6NIjIibdFkIcVef70L9JH8bicSAZBz4uc9ehglLR7No7fZb2MVBaj9hmBn9lrQECM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"display: block;line-height: 1.5;font-size: 24px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-weight: bold;margin: 80px auto 40px auto;width: fit-content;color: #407600;text-align: center;padding: 0 1em;border-bottom: 8px solid #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">短视频自动发布工具</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">熟悉我们的朋友都知道，「十字路口」每期视频播客不只是发一条——正片要发，切片也要发，小红书、视频号、抖音三个平台都得覆盖。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">算下来一期内容少说也要分发七八条。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们自己写了一个自动化工具来干这件事，Python 后端加 Chrome 扩展，一次搞定多平台多视频的发布。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6324074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"501622966\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3194d2be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqnvRiauogTH3m6QJCW0jFyTrz1yqic2yITK2V8cEIBUWg8cyt0IylTeRakLtwlX0yib29pPwVow1DYbCEib34QjeygKXotr1dRIdDM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622971\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f2f9e99&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fa16Y4PLxPql7Qkk8ia37HNFK1WtyibHcicdIwWm5HXvV5uxic1UgbRTFeK8fwUJ7gqvFgtGwxanOgt5dUQb9HCpUwPicKQuOR6tFyThGDGXWchyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次让 M2.7 在这个工具的基础上做一轮功能迭代：</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">补上封面自动适配。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">三个平台的封面比例各不相同，之前都是手动裁三次。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个任务天然是一个多 Skill 串联的压力测试：读取视频源、识别平台差异、裁切封面、填写标题、设置定时发布。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一步都是独立的能力调用，全部串起来才能跑通一次完整分发。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是 M2.7 在</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">「指令遵循」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">和</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">「复杂任务编排」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">上的一次真实考验</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们来看看这个多skill串联的情况下，M2.7完成的情况：</span></p>\n   <div data-video-src=\"\" data-video-thumb=\"https://file.notion.so/f/f/b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d/10dbd9bb-5731-47b7-8c8c-ade6de024898/3月18日(6).mov_thumbnail.jpg?table=block&amp;id=3278e8f5-8ed1-8018-a63c-f43b01ab7e73&amp;spaceId=b9a67ef4-e03f-4d90-8b0f-570daf73564d&amp;expirationTimestamp=1774000800000&amp;signature=jKV-yW47C02uHcGlInY0OuVcm9DTvAIYhaHsVkP_wH4\" style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\">\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上录屏全程自动化，零人工点击。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">可以看到它在处理视频号时，自动识别出封面有两种尺寸要求，做了差异化处理。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 15px 0;text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"501622968\" data-ratio=\"0.3537037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 10px;display: inline-block;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a434e105&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqmocLqBXdnlcPiapEiaRz5cUAjgibgSawBFmszT2Q6VZaJEvwwyRysOyIBFtJGyhdtQjrVA3bhMybLg7fRIXnIwSwSYKliaZMWnE3k%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">🚥&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这三个项目，都是我们自己的工具，自己的 Bug，自己的工作流。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">M2.7 跑下来，体感上最明显的变化有两个：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、面对真实工程问题时，排查路径像一个</span><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">有经验的开发者</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">而不是一个搜索引擎</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">二、多 Skill 串联的场景下，上下文保持得比 M2.5 稳了不少</span></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">回到最开头我们的判断，为什么说这次 M2.7 的更新，和之前「模型变强了」的故事不太一样呢？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它没有在某个榜单上刷出一个惊人的数字，三个项目 跑下来也不是零瑕疵——有些 corner case 它确实还覆盖不到。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但和之前几个版本比，最明显的变化不是</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 118, 0);\">「能做到更多事」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而是</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(50, 120, 71);\">「做得更稳、更像一个熟手了」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些能力提升的背后，有一个细节值得单独说：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax 技术博客里提到，M2.7 的 Agent 脚手架有一部分是模型自己优化的！全程自主跑了 100+ 轮迭代循环，效果提升 30%。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 MLE Bench 的 22 道 Kaggle 竞赛题上拿了 9 金 5 银 1 铜，仅次于 Opus 4.6 和 GPT-5.4。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说，我们在这三个项目里感受到的</span><strong style=\"white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">「更稳、更像老手」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，不完全是人调出来的，有一部分是模型自己迭代出来的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不到五个月，四个版本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当一个模型不只是等着人来优化它，而是开始自己优化自己的时候，迭代速度的意义就变了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;white-space:pre-line;letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-bottom:1em;font-size:15px;line-height:26px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, 'PingFang SC', Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all;font-weight: 600;color: #407600;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不再只是线性的，而是开始有复利了</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501622983\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8310508a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fa16Y4PLxPqkPqAcnZsTQTFOZiaZVQbh645Fcq9HsgTDqPTRVkficLMvzTzo0c0R8sbNZ9vUeSzNkPrnMKS2dicm5HQpMCPMfdYJn8nUftCMWdE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过三个实战案例展示了 MiniMax M2.7 在真实内容工作流中的表现，强调其在复杂任务编排和工程排查上的“熟手”特质。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过三个实战案例展示了 MiniMax M2.7 在真实内容工作流中的表现，强调其在复杂任务编排和工程排查上的“熟手”特质。",
  "summary": "文章详细记录了“十字路口”团队利用 MiniMax M2.7 优化其内容生产全链路的过程。通过开发 Notion 转公众号排版插件、构建播客监控下载工具以及实现短视频自动分发三个具体项目，验证了 M2.7 在指令遵循、多工具（Skill）串联及自主工程排查方面的显著进步。作者指出，M2.7 的核心提升在于从“能做”向“稳健”和“专业”的转变，并特别提到了模型通过自主迭代优化 Agent 脚手架的能力，预示了 AI 迭代正进入复利阶段。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "M2.7 在真实工程排查中表现出类似资深开发者的逻辑路径。",
      "explanation": "模型不再只是简单生成代码，而是能通过命令行启动 Chrome 远程调试，利用 CDP 协议抓取 DOM 并自主分析渲染逻辑，展现了极强的自主调试与环境感知能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "多 Skill 串联能力显著增强，支持复杂任务的自动化闭环。",
      "explanation": "在短视频分发案例中，模型能自动识别不同平台的封面尺寸差异并进行适配，同时完成标题填写与定时发布，证明了其在长链条、多步骤任务中的上下文保持能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 模型的迭代正从线性增长转向由模型驱动的自主复利阶段。",
      "explanation": "MiniMax 提到 M2.7 的 Agent 脚手架部分由模型自主优化完成，这种“模型优化模型”的闭环将极大加速技术演进速度，使其表现出超越人工调优的稳健性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "面对真实工程问题时，排查路径像一个有经验的开发者而不是一个搜索引擎。",
    "最明显的变化不是‘能做到更多事’，而是‘做得更稳、更像一个熟手了’。",
    "当一个模型不只是等着人来优化它，而是开始自己优化自己的时候，迭代速度的意义就变了。它不再只是线性的，而是开始有复利了。"
  ],
